data.description:
Back on the market at no fault to sellers! Sellers to pay 2.5% of closing costs.
This bright and airy 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath house is the perfect place to call home. It features a spacious living area with plenty of natural light, a fully-equipped kitchen with stainless steel appliances, a dinning area perfect for family dinners, and a large backyard with plenty of outdoor space for entertaining. Each of the bedrooms are generously sized, perfect for any use you decide. Other notable features include an attached garage, an easy-to-maintain front and backyard, and a convenient location close to shopping, dining, and entertainment and walking distance from Wayside Elementary! This home is move-in ready and waiting for a new family to make it their own.
